Place is clean, service is good, foods are good, luckily this restaurant is located in Tuen Mun, we can have such a good food in this small town. 

Risotto should be very creamy, however the Tomato Seafoods risotto seems not that creamy, but the taste not bad (a bit spicy). Pizza is good, restaurant is cozy. No need to queue.

Spaghetti is good, drinks is good.
But the environment is just alright.

reviews.text: 食物5星，不提供免費水扣2星，而附款後要求亦不會發收據或手寫單扣2星，需要收據報銷的要留意。
蕃茄海鮮意粉 🤪

食物質素為中上，食材新鮮，即叫即煮，配搭有心思，令食客有豐富的味覺體驗。四粒星。

價錢方面原本是物超所值，都是四粒星；可惜最近改為不提供免費食水，最低要以$8購買樽裝水，令食客主觀上感到吝嗇。其實成本上漲可以理解，寧可店方堂堂正正加價十元八塊，換取光顧用餐的整體滿足感。因此倒扣一粒星。

Place is clean, service is good, foods are good, luckily this restaurant is located in Tuen Mun, we can have such a good food in this small town. 

Risotto should be very creamy, however the Tomato Seafoods risotto seems not that creamy, but the taste not bad (a bit spicy). Pizza is good, restaurant is cozy. No need to queue.
手工醬汁意式食品，款式多，現點現做燉飯與麵。
